/ Team chat input form — extracted as partial so send_team_chat.turbo_stream.erb can re-render it blank
/ Replaced: form_tag with remote: true → form_with (Turbo handles AJAX submission)
- if @current_user
  - chat_display_name = defined?(display_name) ? display_name : (@current_user.first_name || @current_user.username)
  = form_with(url: send_team_chat_solution_path(solution), data: { controller: 'loading', action: 'submit->loading#submit' }) do |f|
    = hidden_field_tag 'display_name', chat_display_name, id: nil
    = hidden_field_tag 'avatar', @current_user.image.thumb, id: nil
    = text_field_tag 'chat', nil, id: nil, autocomplete: :off, aria: {label: 'Team chat message'}
- else
  %p.xw-text-muted.team-chat__anon-prompt
    = link_to 'Sign in', login_path
    to chat with the team
